import React from 'react'
import { Col, Container, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'
import UserSideBar from '../../components/User/UserSideBar'

const UserAllOrdersPage = () => {
  return (
    <Container >
    <Row className='py-3'>
        <Col sm="3" xs="2" md="2">
            <UserSideBar />
        </Col>

        <Col sm="9" xs="10" md="10">
          {/* <UserAllOrder /> */}
        </Col>
    </Row>
</Container>
  )
}

export default UserAllOrdersPage
